    * 0754f23 Offload temp file removal to a clean_temp() function
        (Josh Cepek <josh.cepek@usa.net>)

    * 1c90df9 Fix incorrect handling of invalid --use-algo option
        (Josh Cepek <josh.cepek@usa.net>)

    * c86289b Fix batch-mode handling with changes in e75ad75
        (Josh Cepek <josh.cepek@usa.net>)

