    * 8b1fe01 Support OpenSSL-0.9.8 with the EXTRA_EXTS feature
        (Josh Cepek <josh.cepek@usa.net>)

    * d5516d5 Windows: make builds easier by using a matching dir structure
        (Josh Cepek <josh.cepek@usa.net>)

